---
Set repeat mode

Usage: spotuify repeat [OPTIONS] <STATE>

Arguments:
  <STATE>  Repeat state [possible values: off, context, track]

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for the mutation receipt [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
